@startuml
!theme plain
title 02. Hot KV Data Plane
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "vLLM/OpenAI actor" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "Coherence-CE mesh" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "GPU HBM/local DRAM" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "CXL warm tier" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "OpenZFS durable tier" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : KV request
N2 --> N3 : placement
N3 --> N4 : hot decode
N4 --> N5 : warm staging

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
